section.single.modal.content
  h1 Open Wallet
  p.literal Enter the username and password that was used to encrypt your wallet below.
  form
    label(for='login_username') Username
    input#register_username(name='register_username', type='text')
    label(for='login_password') Password
    input#register_password(name='register_password', type='password')
    label.storageinfo
      | Fetch your wallet from:
      strong  Payward Inc. 
      a(href='#') change
    p.literal.hint
      | Your information will be stored with Payward, lorem ipsum et dolor sit amet.
    div.submitsection
      button.btn.btn-info(type='submit') Go
      p.literal
        | You are responsible for safeguarding your login information.<br>
        | Ripple can not recover your username or password.<br>
        strong Write down your master key. 
        a(href='#') Learn how
    p.literal
      | New to Ripple? 
      a(href='#register') Create a wallet
